description:
British salesman Gregory Kirk's sister Sophie goes missing and his only lead is a photo of Sophie with an ISIS general. Posing as an investigative journalist, Kirk hires a troubled ex-Army Ranger, Bryce Daniels, to help him find her. As they trek through the desolate, war-torn wilderness of Iraq battling terrorists and their own dark secrets, they realize that their quest is not only to save Sophie, but also to seek salvation themselves. Inspired by true events. 

Starring Jacob Dufour, T.L. Bridger, Wayne E. Brown

Viewer discretion advised for violence.
